videos.headline: Washington RB Gaskin can't be stopped on 65-yard TD run
videos.description: Washington RB Myles Gaskin takes the handoff and goes 65 yards to give the Huskies a 21-0 lead over Oregon.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington RB Gaskin can't be stopped on 65-yard TD run) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ross gets foot down in nick of time on 15-yard TD
videos.description: Washington WR John Ross and QB Jake Browning display impeccable timing on a 15-yard touchdown pass and catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ross gets foot down in nick of time on 15-yard TD) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington WR Pettis makes sensational one-handed TD grab
videos.description: Jake Browning throws to Dante Pettis, who makes a spectacular one-handed catch in the end zone to put Washington up 56-14 over Oregon.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington WR Pettis makes sensational one-handed TD grab) 2016/10/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington crushes Oregon behind Browning's eight total TDs
videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning throws for 306 yards and six touchdowns while rushing for two more in a 70-21 victory against Oregon, snapping a 12-game losing streak against the Ducks.
